title: The TryPod: Teaser
description:
Welcome to The TryPod! The Try Guys take a break from their insane lives as digital creators to chat with each other about what they’ve learned from trying anything and everything. In this Teaser, Keith plans his “perfect day”. Spoiler: it involves a pork tamale, and Vegas.
